### Phase 2 Critical Gaps Implemented

| Gap | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Schema Registry** | [SchemaRegistry](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#19-64) class in [bus.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py) — register event types with required fields, version, content hash |
| **Signature Validation** | [compute_event_signature()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#66-75) + [verify_event_signature()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#77-83) — SHA-256 over event fields. All events MUST carry valid signatures |
| **system.backpressure event** | Audit entry emitted when backpressure activates |

### Phase 1 Critical Gaps Implemented

| Gap | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Identity Lifecycle** | [IdentityStatus](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/types.py#13-19) enum + [suspend_identity()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py#164-174), [reinstate_identity()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py#175-198), [revoke_identity()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py#64-67) in [service.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py) — all audited |
| **Module Sandbox** | Restricted builtins execution in [loader.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/module_loader/loader.py) — strips `__import__`, [exec](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#95-121), [eval](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py#95-104), `compile`, `open`, `getattr`, `globals` |
| **Module Versioning** | Manifest [version](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/tests/test_event_bus.py#153-184) and `kernel_compatibility` validated in [loader.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/module_loader/loader.py). Support for [rollback](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py#222-225) capability. |
| **Health Checks** | Automatic instantiation and [healthcheck](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py#238-241) execution for [Module](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/module_loader/loader.py#17-200) classes implementing [ModuleInterface](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py#231-245). |
| **Policy Ordering** | Priority-based evaluation (lower is higher) and "first-deny-wins" logic in [engine.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/policy/engine.py). |
| **Config Schema** | Strict JSON schema validation via `jsonschema` in [main.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/main.py) with nested block support. |
| **Metering Loop** | Proactive `system.budget_exceeded` event emission in [node.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/metering/node.py) when limits are hit or policy denies. |

